The paper deals with the problem of emergent communication in multi-agent reinforcement learning, which involves learning communication protocols between agents to solve tasks. This falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computational linguistics (cs.CL), multi-agent systems (cs.MA), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
